text: Martti Peltoniemi (16 June 1935 - 2 August 1975) was a Finnish wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle lightweight at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1935 births Category:1975 deaths Category:Finnish male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Finland Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from Lappajärvi
